Phase 7 #4 — user picks from queued candidates (vitest infrastructure live; TDD mandatory per Rule 25)

Phase 7 #3 shipped on 2026-05-15 as `8709595`:
- 7-case meetings.test.ts (happy path + minimal-input defaults + Zod rejections + UNAUTHORIZED)
- meetingsRouter.create refactored to import MeetingCreateClientInputSchema from @yelli/shared
- _meeting-form.tsx ported to react-hook-form + zodResolver + shadcn Form primitive
- shadcn Form primitive installed in @yelli/ui (closes UI Rule #4 gap — all future forms use this path)
- 4 new lessons documented: shared schema split, namespace-import lint gotcha, vi.mocked Prisma `as never` cast extension, shadcn Form scoping
- Visual QA Rule 16 deferred — auth-gated route, manual smoke pending next dev-up session

